show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/7F2K3W
show.description:
Once a wealthy young man, he returns to college—not as a victim, but as a storm. Betrayed by childhood love, destroyed by those he trusted, and left for dead, he rises again with a new purpose.
This is a tale of revenge, redemption, and reclaiming identity—where every step forward burns with buried pain.
